description:
Take a look at Sardis from the sky; located in the Manisa Province of western Turkey, near Sart in this Cinematic Aerial Film. When filming for the Lineage 'The 7 Churches of Revelation' series, we captured some incredible views from the skies of Turkey.

🎬 Main Episode: https://youtu.be/xOIpgLfEQDw
📹 Behind the Scenes: https://youtu.be/XrL8MeAe5FI

Sardis - the fifth of the seven Churches of Revelation is located on the road to Philadelphia. It sits below some stunning mountain scenery, and today the city is abandoned and desolate - a fitting fulfilment of a church that is described as being dead. There is some fascinating history connected to this church with powerful lessons for us today.
